snippet: KAUFMAN--Robert. The Palm Beach Country Club expresses its profound sorrow at the passing of its esteemed member, Robert Kaufman, and extends sincere sympathy to his wife, children, grandchildren, and other members of his family. Jeffrey B. Lane, President Warren J. Spector, Secretary 1/3
lead_paragraph: KAUFMAN--Robert. The Palm Beach Country Club expresses its profound sorrow at the passing of its esteemed member, Robert Kaufman, and extends sincere sympathy to his wife, children, grandchildren, and other members of his family. Jeffrey B. Lane, President Warren J. Spector, Secretary 1/3
